c: 11
v: 87
t: Jisuot sigra kawom seurakah Hai Syuʻib peue keuh seumbahyang gata Nyang yue bak gata beu kamoe keubah Peue nyang geuseumah le du-du gata Bek le nyan jinoe nyang kamoe seumah Atawa tatham dum atra kamoe Bek ban heut kamoe meupeugot ulah Keubit nyoe gata ureueng got ate Carong that pike utoh sileupah